@node mystify "What is mystify"

	What is mystify:
	----------------

	- Mystify is MULTITASKING music disk
	- It contains good music from BFB Team's musician.
	- It's capable to run on ANY amiga with KS 1.3 and above.
	- It uses ONLY system fuctions, so if Mystify isn't working with your
	  graphics card, you can't blame me. (I hope :)
	- It can be installed on HD.
	- Doesn't require AGA but can be run on one.
	- Because Mystify uses system's screen, it automacicly supports
	  mode promotions.
	- And the best: It doesn't crash. (Pretty wild, huh :)

@endnode

